  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_RadDrawer1_Content_MainContent_DetailedOutput\"><strong>Recipe Price</strong> 10 sp<br /><strong>Ingredients</strong> 1 basic, 1 special<br /><strong>Preparation</strong> DC 14 Cooking Lore, DC 16 Survival</span><br /><strong>Requirements</strong> Basic Kitchen<br /><strong>Favorite Meal</strong> You sleep extra well, requiring only 6 hours of rest. to get its full benefits.</p><hr /><p><span id=\"ctl00_RadDrawer1_Content_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">Spiced milk is typically made by frothing or taking milk to its curdling point so its hearty and hot, and various spices such as pine nuts, almonds, cardamon, honey and cinnamon are added into it. Different variations of the drink exist, depending on culture, but nothing beats a hot cup of milk with a spiced kick when you're down in the dumps or sick.</span></p><p>Drinkers of spiced milk gain a +1 item bonus to saving throws against emotion and disease effects for 24 hours, or until their next daily preparations, whichever comes first. If they already benefit from an item bonus, increase this item bonus by that amount instead.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.equipment.Item.UzS5CsnOx1jeYRms]{Effect: Spiced Milk}</p>"
